"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-07-26-transfer-greek-club-olympiacos-interested-in-sadiq\", \"text\": \"Published  on  By  Greek Super League club, Olympiacos are interested in Umar Sadiq.  Sadiq is looking to leave LaLiga side, Real Sociedad this summer after struggling to feature regularly for the club last season.  The 27-year-old started 14 out of 34 games for Real Sociedad last season.  According to Greek news outlet, B92 Sport, Olympiacos are keen to add the lanky striker to their squad.  The forward has played for clubs in Italy, the Netherlands, Scotland, Serbia, and Spain in the past.  He has been linked with a number of clubs in Spain including Getafe, Sevilla and Valencia.  Transfer: Muhammad joins Locomotiv Zagreb on five-year contract  NPFL: Remo Stars sign Onuoha deal from Heartland  Transfer: Club Brugge plot move for Fernandez  Transfer: Premier League clubs interested in Nigerian-born goalkeeper  Transfer: Rangers line up summer move for Sanusi  Transfer: Nwabali not concerned over free agent status  Transfer: Onazi moves to Lithuanian club FK Babrungas  Transfer: Barcelona eyes Chelsea's Pedro Neto as alternative to Marcus Rashford  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\"}"